---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title="Atletes Voltedge | Team Elite">
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="bg-black text-white pt-32 pb-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-red-500 block mb-3">ELENCO DE LLEGENDES</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight">
          TEAM <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-red-600">VOLTEDGE</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-sm md:text-base max-w-xl mx-auto">
          L'energia dels qui canvien les regles del joc. Coneix els ambaixadors globals que porten el potencial humà al límit.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-neutral-800 shadow-2xl hover:border-red-600/50 transition group">
          <div class="h-96 bg-neutral-850 relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-950 via-transparent to-transparent z-10"></div>
            <img 
              src="/alex-pereira.png" 
              alt="Alex Pereira - Voltedge Team" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 relative z-20 -mt-10">
            <span class="bg-red-600 text-white font-bold text-[10px] px-2.5 py-1 rounded uppercase tracking-widest">UFC CHAMPION</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mt-3">Alex "Poatan" Pereira</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mt-2 leading-relaxed">
              Mans de pedra i un enfocament glacial. El campió de la UFC personifica la potència pura, el focus absolut i l'energia implacable que defineixen Voltedge a l'octàgon.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-neutral-800 shadow-2xl hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition group">
          <div class="h-96 bg-neutral-850 relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-950 via-transparent to-transparent z-10"></div>
            <img 
              src="/vini-jr.png" 
              alt="Vini Jr. - Voltedge Team" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 relative z-20 -mt-10">
            <span class="bg-yellow-500 text-black font-bold text-[10px] px-2.5 py-1 rounded uppercase tracking-widest">FOOTBALL ELITE</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mt-3">Vinícius Jr.</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mt-2 leading-relaxed">
              Velocitat elèctrica, descaradura i màgia pura sobre la gespa. L'energia activa de Voltedge és el motor darrere de cada esprint i ball de la superestrella mundial.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-neutral-800 shadow-2xl hover:border-blue-500/50 transition group">
          <div class="h-96 bg-neutral-850 relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-neutral-950 via-transparent to-transparent z-10"></div>
            <img 
              src="/carlos-alcaraz.png" 
              alt="Carlos Alcaraz - Voltedge Team" 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 relative z-20 -mt-10">
            <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold text-[10px] px-2.5 py-1 rounded uppercase tracking-widest">TENNIS CHAMP</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mt-3">Carlos Alcaraz</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mt-2 leading-relaxed">
              Intensitat salvatge punt a punt. Cap, cor, collons i pura fúria Voltedge per aguantar partits èpics de cinc sets a la pista de tennis sense baixar les revolucions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>